  "instructions": [
    "Heat the bacon fat or oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and cook for 1-2 minutes, until fragrant.",
    "Add the dried red chillies and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the rice and cook for 2-3 minutes, until lightly toasted.",
    "Add the chicken broth and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 18-20 minutes.",
    "Stir in the coconut milk and cook for another 2-3 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot and garnish with chopped scallions or cilantro, if desired."
